snippet.title: Blob The Klex Demo-Official Playthrough
snippet.description:
ITCH.IO DOWNLOAD LINK:
https://blobtheklex.itch.io/blob-the-klex

After a long time in the oven i can finally reveal what i have been working on with my friends at uni.
Blob The Klex is a Cute and simple 3D Platformer. This has been a fun first game to work on and i hope i can work on more in the future.

Links:
Blob the Klex instagramm
https://www.instagram.com/blobtheklex/
My lovley team mates :)
